---
title: Grilled Beyond Meat® Meatloaf Burgers with Sweet Potatoes and Green Onion Mayo
description: The best of mom's meatloaf and a Beyond Meat® burger are combined between toasted buns! Zesty green onion mayo is a great dipper for barbecued sweet potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-grilles-au-pain-de-viande-102f94bd-7ab649f3.jpg
